Gravatar JSF Component

Example
-------

<gr:avatar xmlns:gr="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar" email="foo@example.com" size="128" />

Deferred image loading
----------------------

If you want to use deferred image loading, please make sure you have included jQuery and 
the following Javascript:

$("img[data-defer-src]").each(function() {
	$(this).attr('src', $(this).attr("data-defer-src"));
});